anniversary of taylor made in  nelson a taylor started taylor made in  as a canvas business from its very inception it was his vision for the company to take an aggressive stance on product development — unveiling many uniquely creative and original canvas offerings then in  upon the founder’s passing his son willard taylor was named company president it was from this point forward and under willard’s leadership that taylor made began to grow and expand rapidly willard taylor brought with him a decisive commitment to the burgeoning recreational boating market along with a quest to push design and technology ever forward with new applications processes and products from the introduction of the first wraparound acrylic windshield for motorboats in  to the first curved tempered safety glass windshield to manufacturing the first vinyl fenders ‘guaranteed for the life of your boat’ to countless advancements in glass bending stainless steel welding and other technologies that have defined the modern era of boat windshield design taylor made has been a leader in addressing the unique challenges of the marine market to this day taylor made systems – together with recent acquisitions trend marine products ltd and waterbonnet mfg inc – is the world’s largest manufacturer of marine glazing systems and sets the pace for advancements in the styling and design of boat windshields windows doors hatches power roof systems portlights and more taylor made products is the world’s leading supplier of boat fenders and buoys as well as one of the largest and most innovative suppliers of marine aftermarket products including boat covers bimini tops dock products flags hardware and more taylorbrite® utilizes proprietary technologies such as led and coldcathode lighting to provide advanced lighting systems for marine and other markets its products are setting new records for service life and reliability additionally taylor made has successfully led the way into other areas of the marine marketplace in  marine air systems was established to manufacture highperformance comfortcontrol systems refrigeration systems and more – eventually through the acquisition of marine development corp cruisair and condaria in italy growing into taylor made environmental in  sealand technology was launched to address the needs of marine sanitation — using innovative vacuflush® technology both of these companies flourished as taylor made owned entities for many years before being divested so that the group could focus on its core competencies and technologies these versatile capabilities enable taylor made to compete in a number of other markets taylor made glass systems is a leader in the design and manufacture of curved tempered safety glass for applications in architectural agricultural industrial and other business sectors and taylor made custom products continues to thrive as a leader in the design and fabrication of custom commercial residential and backlit fabric awnings snowmobile covers recreational bags  more the business directives initiated a century ago by nelson a taylor are now carried on by the current generation of taylors – jim taylor board of directors and john taylor secretary – as well as taylor made group executive chairman dennis flint and many other longtime committed executives and associates “solidly grounded in our rich legacy and with our ideals firmly in place we look forward to an exciting future as we continue to diversify and adapt while retaining our dedication to the marine industry” said flint return to taylor made group home page the taylor made group about history offices press patents contact  taylor made group llc gloversville ny  taylormade® the taylor made group™ and the logos and names of member companies and their products as indicated are trademarks or registered trademarks of taylor made group llc in the united states and in other countries except for taylor made glass systems™ which is a trademark of taylor made glass ohio llc in the united states and in other countries